Package: rustinr
Type: Package
Title: R and Rust Integration Devtool
Version: 0.1.0
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3)
Author: Qin Wenfeng
Maintainer: Qin Wenfeng <mail@qinwenfeng.com>
Description: rustr is a Rust library that provides a Rust API to work with R. Write pure Rust code with rustr, and then use rustinr R package to generate Rust interface in R.
License: Apache License 2.0
LazyData: TRUE
SystemRequirements: The Rust package manager Cargo (http://doc.crates.io/) , The Rust compiler rustc (https://www.rust-lang.org/).
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Suggests: testthat
